{
  "texts": [
    "Literature EstimatesWhy Include Literature Estimates?",
    "In addition to performing ablation experiments, we include estimates from the literature for Mixture-of-Experts (MoE) models and tokenization methods.",
    "MoE models are challenging to implement and measure at small scales due to complex routing mechanisms and loss-balancing requirements.",
    "Moreover, there is already substantial literature comparing dense and MoE transformers.Tokenizers also present significant challenges.",
    "Perplexity is inherently tokenizer-dependent."
  ]
}